title: Inslee appoints Dan Pacholke as Secretary of the Washington Department of Corrections (The Office of ...
text: ( Source : The Office of the Governor of the State of Washington ) OLYMPIA - Gov. Jay Inslee today announced he's appointed Dan Pacholke to serve as the new Secretary of Corrections for the State of Washington, effective October 17 , 2015 .
